Get AFL Stats cookie

Source: R/womens_stats.R
get_aflw_cookie.Rd

Replaced with a standard function to return cookies for either mens or womens data

get_aflw_cookie()

Examples

#
if (FALSE) { # \dontrun{
get_aflw_cookie()
# ->
get_aflw_cookie()
} # }
